    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s as close to perfect as it gets. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
